# Model config: GLM-4.7-Flash (UD-Q5_K_XL, MoE)
#
# Rationale:
#   - Zhipu's recommended sampling for GLM-4.7: temp 0.7, top-p 1.0, min-p 0.01.
#   - q8_0 KV cache (launcher default) keeps the KV small so more memory is free for
#     the MoE weights + a long context.

: "${MODEL:=GLM-4.7-Flash/GLM-4.7-Flash-UD-Q5_K_XL.gguf}"

LLAMA_ARGS+=(--temp 0.7 --top-p 1.0 --min-p 0.01)
